<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Modern Attractive UI</title>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: #f4f6fb;
            color: #333;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        header {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2575fc;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #444;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover,
        nav a.active {
            background: #2575fc;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Container */
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container h2 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #222;
        }

        .container p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        /* Cards */
        .card-box {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f1f6ff);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            width: 240px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .card i {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #2575fc;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 19px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #222;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            background: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 18px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
        }
    </style>
    
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>My Website</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="active"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home</a>
            <a href="/about"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> About</a>
            <a href="/product"><i class="fas fa-box"></i> Products</a>
            <a href="/blog"><i class="fas fa-blog"></i> Blog</a>
            <a href="/contact"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to Our Website üåê</h2>
        <p>Explore our sections below and discover more about us.</p>
        <div class="card-box">
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                <a href="/about">
                    <h3>About Us</h3>
                </a>
                <p>Learn more about our team, our journey, and our values.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fas fa-box"></i>
                <a href="/product">
                    <h3>Products</h3>
                </a>
                <p>Check out our latest offerings, deals, and collections.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fas fa-blog"></i>
                <a href="/blog">
                    <h3>Blog</h3>
                </a>
                <p>Read the latest news, articles, and insights from us.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                <a href="/contact">
                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                </a>
                <p>Get in touch with our team anytime, anywhere.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        ¬© 2025 My Website. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

</body>

</html>